title: Managing Custom VM Extensions
owner: Ops Manager
---

This topic describes how to add, delete, apply, and list custom virtual machine extensions using the Ops Manager API.

Documentation for this feature was added in Pivotal Cloud Foundry v2.1 and does not exist for earlier versions.

For information about this feature in current versions of the documentation, see [Managing Custom VM Extensions](http://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/customizing/custom-vm-extensions.html).

